original_title: The Seven Secrets of Successful Stamping
overview: Dee's legendary zeal is contagious! Periodicals have called her "the head cheerleader of rubberstamping". Her quest remains to take stamping out of just a stamp pad mentality and into the extraordinary world of multicolored art.
tagline: Clear instruction in rubberstamping with brush art marking pens for stunning effects... Vivid, pure, even blended colors.
title: The Seven Secrets of Successful Stamping
